725837f-a.title: Queens: 124th Street - 21st Avenue
725837f-a.text:
124th Street, east side, adjoining (to the south) 21st
Avenue, showing two frame houses. These homes were owned,
in 1873, by Mrs. Klok (left) and C. Elen.
P. L. Sperr  March 16, 1932
NO REPRODUCTIONS
